{"version":1,"entries":{"person_2503942_translations":{"at":1772647160341,"data":{"id":2503942,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wang Wanzhong","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"王婉中，1992年1月31日出生于北京，毕业于北京电影学院，中国内地女演员。 2011年，出演个人首部电影《青春的季节》，从此正式进入演艺圈。2013年，因在尔冬升执导的青春励志片《我是路人甲》中饰演兰贵人而崭露头角，随后，还参演了古装爱情片《宫锁沉香》。2014年，主演爱情喜剧片《奇葩追梦》。2015年，主演励志喜剧片《活宝》；同年，出演历史战争片《大轰炸》。2016年，参演古装传奇剧《开封府传奇》。2017年，参演抗日谍战剧《火线孤城》。2018年6月，主演的古装励志爱情网络剧《替嫁公主》开机。","name":"王婉中","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wang Wanzhong","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"王婉中，1992 年 1 月 31 日出生於北京，畢業於北京電影學院，中國內地女演員。\n\n2011 年，出演個人首部電影《青春的季節》，從此正式進入演藝圈。2013 年，因在爾冬升執導的青春勵志片《我是路人甲》中飾演蘭貴人而嶄露頭角，隨後，還參演了古裝愛情片《宮鎖沉香》。2014 年，主演愛情喜劇片《奇葩追夢》。2015 年，主演勵誌喜劇片《活寶》；同年，出演歷史戰爭片《大轟炸》。2016 年，參演古裝傳奇劇《開封府傳奇》。2017 年，參演抗日諜戰劇《火線孤城》。2018 年 6 月，主演的古裝勵志愛情網絡劇《替嫁公主》開機。","name":"王婉中","primary":false}}]}},"person_3813826_translations":{"at":1772647160755,"data":{"id":3813826,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"GR","iso_639_1":"el","name":"ελληνικά","english_name":"Greek","data":{"biography":"Η Wang Nan Nan είναι μια κινέζα ηθοποιός υπό την ομάδα Banana Entertainment.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Wang Nannan","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王楠楠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王楠楠","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"王楠楠","primary":false}}]}},"person_1352662_translations":{"at":1772647162970,"data":{"id":1352662,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"Charlotte Sophie Kirk was born in Kent, England. Her passion for acting began at the age of 11 when she fell in love with the stage. She has since performed in Greek dramas and plays such as \"Agamemnon,\" \"Arturo Ui,\" \"A Christmas Carol,\" \"Oliver Twist,\" and \"Hairspray.\" Having attended the prestigious Italia Conti School of Acting in London, her skills were further refined at The Miskin Theatre and Jigsaw Performing Arts. While studying theatre arts, she appeared in commercials for Nintendo Wii and UK Orange Telecom.\n\nCharlotte also became sought after and was photographed for magazines internationally, in particular by renowned Vogue photographer Patrick Demarchelier.\n\nIn early 2015, Charlotte Kirk landed a starring role in \"Vice\" opposite Bruce Willis and Thomas Jane, a sci-fi futuristic thriller. Charlotte has completed seven feature films, including \"Black Dog Red Dog\" with James Franco, \"Fractured\" with Vinnie Jones, \"Seduced and Abandoned,\" directed by James Toback, and \"Tekken: Kazuya's Revenge,\" where she plays a female assassin.\n\nShe will also be starring as Nicole Brown Simpson in the upcoming feature film \"An American Mystery\".\n\n\"Gone With The Wind\" is her all-time favorite film, as she admires strong heroines. Charlotte presently resides in Los Angeles and is managed by Endorse Management Group and Headline Talent Agency.","name":"Charlotte Kirk","primary":true}},{"iso_3166_1":"CZ","iso_639_1":"cs","name":"Český","english_name":"Czech","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"DE","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","iso_639_1":"ja","name":"日本語","english_name":"Japanese","data":{"biography":"","name":"シャーロット・カーク","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"FR","iso_639_1":"fr","name":"Français","english_name":"French","data":{"biography":"Actrice, productrice et scénariste britannique, Charlotte Kirk se prend de passion pour le théâtre et le cinéma dès l’âge de onze ans. Dès lors, elle joue dans des pièces amateurs, avant de perfectionner son jeu dans plusieurs écoles prestigieuses dont celle de Lee Strasberg à New York. Elle débute à l’écran en 2013 dans des rôles secondaires. Toutefois, on la découvre vraiment dans Vice (2015), un thriller de science-fiction avec Bruce Willis. Elle obtient ensuite un tout petit rôle dans Ocean’s 8 (2018).\n\nC’est en 2018 qu’elle fait la rencontre du réalisateur Neil Marshall et qu’ils entretiennent une liaison. Le nouveau couple choisit de s’associer pour créer leur maison de production et développer des projets en commun.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"AT","iso_639_1":"de","name":"Deutsch","english_name":"German","data":{"biography":"","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"夏洛特·柯克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"Британская актриса, сценарист и продюсер","name":"Шарлотта Кирк","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"UA","iso_639_1":"uk","name":"Український","english_name":"Ukrainian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Шарлотта Кірк","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TH","iso_639_1":"th","name":"ภาษาไทย","english_name":"Thai","data":{"biography":"","name":"ชาร์ลอ ตต์","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"TW","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"","name":"夏綠蒂·柯克","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HY","iso_639_1":"hy","name":"","english_name":"Armenian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Շառլոտա Քիրք","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"KR","iso_639_1":"ko","name":"한국어/조선말","english_name":"Korean","data":{"biography":"","name":"샬롯 커크","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1